<Layout title="Storage in Brisbane Homes: Built-in Wardrobes, Walk-in Robes, and How Storage Affects Value | Daniel Gierach Property" description="Storage is one of the cheapest ways to lift perceived value before listing. Here is how built-in wardrobes, walk-in robes, pantries, and external storage shape buyer impressions in Brisbane.">

<article style="background:var(--color-surface-0);min-height:100vh;">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <div style="background:#0a0806;padding:8rem 0 3rem;">
    <div class="max-w-[780px] mx-auto px-8">
